_sText:
Hello, everyone!

This is (kind of) my first map using Source SDK.  I've made maps before, but this is the only map I've actually made a decent effort on.

If you'd like another version or have requests and such, feel free to let me know!

Please leave comments with constructive criticism, etc.  I'm new to FPSBanana, so I'm not really great with this kind of stuff yet.

Enjoy!

(P.S I want this map to become popular so upload it to your server if you'd like ^_-)


Thank you!

-XantaX


EDIT: I forgot to mention, theres a secret in the map.  I won't give it away, but here's a hint:

Breakable bricks
